<eesti>Seaduse reguleerimisala </eesti>
<inglise>Scope of application of Act </inglise>
<eesti>(1) K&auml;esolev seadus s&auml;testab tsiviilk&auml;ibes oleva l&otilde;hkematerjali k&auml;itlemise ja k&auml;ibe &otilde;iguslikud alused. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) This Act provides the legal bases for the handling of and trade in explosive substances for civilian purposes. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) K&auml;esoleva seaduse m&otilde;istes on l&otilde;hkematerjal l&otilde;hkeaine, p&uuml;rotehniline aine ning nimetatud ainet sisaldav toode ja vahend. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) For the purposes of this Act, explosive substances are explosives, pyrotechnic substances, and articles or devices containing such substances. </inglise>
<eesti>(3) K&auml;esolevat seadust ei kohaldata: </eesti>
<inglise>(3) This Act does not apply to: </inglise>
<eesti>1) kaitsej&otilde;udude, politsei, piirivalve, P&auml;&auml;steameti, s&otilde;jav&auml;estatud p&auml;&auml;ste&uuml;ksuste ja Eesti Riigikaitse Akadeemia k&auml;sutuses olevale l&otilde;hkematerjalile, v&auml;lja arvatud juhud, kui need on k&auml;esolevas seaduses nimetatud; </eesti>
<inglise>1) explosive substances at the disposal of the Defence Forces, the Police, the Border Guard, the Rescue Service Administration, militarised rescue units or the Estonian National Defence and Public Services Academy, except for in the cases specified in this Act; </inglise>
<eesti>2) l&otilde;hkematerjali veole auto-, raudtee-, &otilde;hu- ja veetranspordiga, kui k&auml;esolev seadus ei s&auml;testa teisiti. </eesti>
<inglise>2) the carriage of explosive substances by road, rail, air or water, unless otherwise provided for in this Act. </inglise>
<eesti>(4) K&auml;esolev seadus laieneb tsiviilk&auml;ibes kasutatava l&otilde;hkeaine taastootmisele lahingumoonast ja p&uuml;rotehniliste toodete komplekteerimisele. </eesti>
<inglise>(4) This Act applies to the recycling of ammunition into explosives for civilian purposes and to the assembly of pyrotechnic articles. </inglise>
<eesti>(5) K&auml;esolev seadus laieneb l&otilde;hkematerjali sisaldavale laskemoonale ainult selle t&ouml;&ouml;stusliku valmistamise osas. </eesti>
<inglise>(5) This Act applies to ammunition which contains explosive substances only with regard to the industrial production thereof. </inglise>
<eesti>F&uuml;&uuml;silise isiku poolt kodusel teel oma tarbeks padrunite valmistamist padrunikomponentidest ja laskemoona k&auml;itlemist teistel juhtudel reguleerib relvaseadus. </eesti>
<inglise>The home production of cartridges from cartridge components for own use by natural persons and all other handling of ammunition is regulated by the Weapons Act. </inglise>
<eesti>(13.06.2001 j&otilde;ust.01.01.2002 - RT I 2001, 65, 377) </eesti>
